/n 3 def
/ExtAngle 360 n div def
 /polygon{
 gsave
newpath
moveto
n 1 sub{
side 0 rlineto % add line
ExtAngle rotate
} repeat
closepath 
stroke
grestore
 } def


/h 86.6 def
/w 240 def

/rectangle {
gsave
newpath % start in top right corner with drawing
 moveto
w 2 div x add h 2 div y add moveto
-1 w mul 0 rlineto
